org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters

Class ImpinjDISpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.Custom
          • org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters.ImpinjDISpec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessCommandOpSpec, AccessCommandOpSpecResult, SpecParameter

    public class ImpinjDISpec
extends Custom
implements SpecParameter
    This parameter is specified in an ROSpec and details direction operation.Only one ImpinjDISpec may be specified in an ROSpec. When specifed, no other spec parameters can be present in the ROSpec. See also
